data.description: A very nice community with lots to offer! This home has been updated with a new 13K roof in 2020, New AC 2021, All new Windows over 4K, painted 2019, New shed with true foundation, water heater 2021, new refrigerator, new electrical panel W/ 30 Amp hookup for RV or Boat AND the best part they added top of line $40,000 in new Solar system(that seller will be paying off for buyer......SO ITS FREE to new buyer)!!! Just try and find all this with ALMOST no electric bills for under 300K in East Valley. HOA(community center, beautiful pool, shuffle board and more is ELECTIVE) You can either enjoy all the benefits on The COMMUNITY HOA at 250.00 annually) or Buyer does not have to(its truly elective for new buyer). Community & this home is well taken care of.
